(Project Documentation) Tj
T*
(Media Controller \(Flask + Slideshow Engine\)) Tj
T*
(Generated on: 2026-03-28 16:04) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Project Overview) Tj
T*
(This project provides a web-based control panel for running an image/video slideshow on) Tj
T*
(Raspberry Pi.) Tj
T*
(Users can upload media, set photo duration, start/stop playback, and manage media files from) Tj
T*
(phone or PC.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2. Core Features) Tj
T*
(Web UI with responsive controls for START, STOP, upload, delete, and interval updates.) Tj
T*
(Playback engine supports photos \(.png/.jpg/.jpeg\) and videos \(.mp4/.mov/.avi\).) Tj
T*
(Background process control using PID tracking and safe process termination.) Tj
T*
(Pending-delete handling to avoid file conflicts while media is playing.) Tj
T*
(Service-friendly deployment for Raspberry Pi with auto-start support via systemd.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3. Scalable Folder Structure) Tj
T*
(Py/) Tj
T*
(  app.py                               # web entrypoint) Tj
T*
(  slideshow.py                         # slideshow entrypoint) Tj
T*
(  install_shop_service.sh              # one-time Raspberry Pi setup) Tj
T*
(  README_RASPBERRY_PI.md               # deployment guide) Tj
T*
(  requirements.txt) Tj
T*
(  media_controller/) Tj
T*
(    __init__.py) Tj
T*
(    constants.py                       # centralized paths/constants) Tj
T*
(    config_store.py                    # config read/write) Tj
T*
(    pending_store.py                   # pending delete store + path safety) Tj
T*
(    process_manager.py                 # pid/process lifecycle) Tj
T*
(    networking.py                      # LAN IP helper) Tj
T*
(    web.py                             # Flask routes and app lifecycle) Tj
T*
(    slideshow_runner.py                # slideshow playback engine) Tj
T*
(    templates/) Tj
T*
(      index.html                       # UI template) Tj
T*
(  photos/                              # uploaded images) Tj
T*
(  videos/                              # uploaded videos) Tj
T*
(  config.json) Tj
T*
(  pending_delete.json) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4. How To Run \(Development\)) Tj
T*
(1. Install dependencies: pip install -r requirements.txt) Tj
T*
(2. Start web app: python app.py) Tj
T*
(3. Open browser: http://<device-ip>:5000) Tj
T*
(4. Use START button to launch slideshow process.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5. Raspberry Pi Shop Deployment) Tj
T*
(1. cd /path/to/project) Tj
T*
(2. chmod +x install_shop_service.sh) Tj
T*
(3. bash install_shop_service.sh) Tj
T*
(4. Open: http://<raspberry-pi-ip>:5000) Tj
T*
(Service name: media-controller.service) Tj
ET
endstream
